title: 'Good Quality'
body: 'Quality is good but quite overpriced. 2 pcs in description means 1 bucket and 1 mug I confused it by considering 2 sets of bucket and mug. However satisfied with quality.'

title: 'Leakage in the bucket after 2 weeks of usage'
body: 'Donot buy this product. I used it for 2 weeks and the bucket suddenly started leaking. Low quality product at such a high price.'

title: 'Very overpriced'
body: 'It’s very overpriced with a ordinary quality plastic so returned it'
